  (3441, 3, 23, 34, 'Speak unto the children of Israel, saying, The fifteenth day of this seventh month shall be the feast of tabernacles for seven days unto the LORD.', '0~01696~ 3~01121~ 5~03478~, 6~0559~, 8~06240~ 9~02568~* 10~03117~ 13~07637~ 14~02320~ [15 16] 18~02282~ 20~05521~ [21] 22~07651~ 23~03117~ 26~03068~.'),
