  (25547, 42, 13, 16, 'And ought not this woman, being a daughter of Abraham, whom Satan hath bound, lo, these eighteen years, be loosed from this bond on the sabbath day?', '0~1161~ 1~1163~ 2~3756~ 4~5026~, 5~5607~ 7~2364~ 9~11~, 10~3739~ 11~4567~ 13~1210~, 14~2400~, 16~3638~ 17~1176~* 18~2532~* 19~2094~, 21~3089~ 22~575~ 23~5127~ 24~1199~ 27~4521~ 28~2250~?'),
