  (29349, 49, 5, 29, 'For no man ever yet hated his own flesh; but nourisheth and cherisheth it, even as the Lord the church:', '0~1063~ 2~3762~ 4~4218~ 5~3404~ 7~1438~ 8~4561~; 9~235~ 10~1625~ 11~2532~ 12~2282~ 13~846~, 15~2532~ 16~2531~ 17~2962~ 19~1577~:'),
