  (7994, 9, 30, 9, 'So David went, he and the six hundred men that were with him, and came to the brook Besor, where those that were left behind stayed.', '1~01732~ 2~03212~, 6~08337~ 7~03967~ 8~0376~ [10] 14~0935~ 17~05158~ 18~01308~, 24~03498~ 25~05975~.'),
