  (18187, 23, 28, 14, 'Wherefore hear the word of the LORD, ye scornful men, that rule this people which is in Jerusalem.', '&para; 1~08085~ 3~01697~ 6~03068~, 8~03944~ 9~0582~, 11~04910~ 13~05971~ [15] 17~03389~.'),
