  (26496, 43, 9, 41, 'Jesus said unto them, If ye were blind, ye should have no sin: but now ye say, We see; therefore your sin remaineth.', '0~2424~ 1~2036~ 3~846~, 4~1487~ 6~2258~ 7~5185~, 9~302~ 10~2192~ 11~3756~ 12~266~: 13~1161~ 14~3568~ 16~3004~ 17~3754~,* 19~991~; 20~3767~ 21~5216~ 22~266~ 23~3306~.'),
