  (4646, 4, 29, 32, 'And on the seventh day seven bullocks, two rams, and fourteen lambs of the first year without blemish:', '3~07637~ 4~03117~ 5~07651~ 6~06499~, 7~08147~ 8~0352~, [9] 10~06240~ 11~0702~* 12~03532~ 15~01121~ 16~08141~ 18~08549~:'),
  (23694, 40, 16, 12, 'Then understood they how that he bade them not beware of the leaven of bread, but of the doctrine of the Pharisees and of the Sadducees.', '0~5119~ 2~4920~ 4~3754~ 6~2036~ [7] 8~3756~ 9~4337~ 10~575~ 12~2219~ 14~740~, 15~235~ 16~575~ 18~1322~ 21~5330~ 22~2532~ 25~4523~.'),
