  (29840, 55, 1, 15, 'This thou knowest, that all they which are in Asia be turned away from me; of whom are Phygellus and Hermogenes.', '&para; 0~5124~ 2~1492~, 3~3754~ 4~3956~ 8~1722~ 9~773~ 13~654~ 14~3165~; 16~3739~ 17~2076~ 18~5436~ 19~2532~ 20~2061~.'),
