  (27056, 44, 4, 18, 'And they called them, and commanded them not to speak at all nor teach in the name of Jesus.', '0~2532~ 2~2564~ 3~846~, 5~3853~ 6~846~ 7~3361~ 9~5350~ 11~2527~ 12~3366~ 13~1321~ 14~1909~ 16~3686~ 18~2424~.'),
