  (11698, 14, 24, 12, 'And the king and Jehoiada gave it to such as did the work of the service of the house of the LORD, and hired masons and carpenters to repair the house of the LORD, and also such as wrought iron and brass to mend the house of the LORD.', '2~04428~ 4~03077~ 5~05414~ 10~06213~ 12~04399~ 15~05656~ 18~01004~ 21~03068~, 23~07936~ 24~02672~ 26~02796~ 28~02318~ 30~01004~ 33~03068~, 38~02796~ 39~01270~ 41~05178~ 43~02388~ 45~01004~ 48~03068~.'),
  (19833, 24, 35, 1, 'The word which came unto Jeremiah from the LORD in the days of Jehoiakim the son of Josiah king of Judah, saying,', '&para; 1~01697~ 5~03414~ 8~03068~ 11~03117~ 13~03079~ 15~01121~ 17~02977~ 18~04428~ 20~03063~, 21~0559~,'),
  (22045, 27, 10, 21, 'But I will shew thee that which is noted in the scripture of truth: and there is none that holdeth with me in these things, but Michael your prince.', '0~061~ 3~05046~ 8~07559~ 11~03791~ 13~0571~: [15 16] 17~0259~ 19~02388~ 26~04317~ 28~08269~.'),
  (6941, 7, 15, 5, 'And when he had set the brands on fire, he let them go into the standing corn of the Philistines, and burnt up both the shocks, and also the standing corn, with the vineyards and olives.', '4~01197~ 6~03940~ 8~0784~, [11] 12~07971~ 16~07054~ 19~06430~, 22~01197~ 25~01430~, 30~07054~, 33~03754~ [34] 35~02132~.'),
  (11072, 13, 25, 18, 'The eleventh to Azareel, he, his sons, and his brethren, were twelve:', '1~06240~ 2~06249~ 3~05832~, [4] 6~01121~, 9~0251~, [10] 11~06240~ 12~08147~:*'),
  (15672, 19, 106, 12, 'Then believed they his words; they sang his praise.', '1~0539~ 4~01697~; 6~07891~ 8~08416~.'),
